      "commercial_conditions": "Quotation Validity: This quotation is valid for 30 calendar days from the date of issue.\nScope of Work: The quotation covers only the deliverables specifically listed in this proposal. Any additional work requested by the Client shall be treated as a variation and quoted separately.\nPayment Terms: Payments shall be made according to the agreed milestone schedule. All invoices are payable within 15 calendar days from the invoice date.\nProject Commencement: Work will commence only after receipt of the agreed advance payment (where applicable) and all required technical inputs from the Client.\nEngineering Inputs: The Client shall provide all necessary drawings, specifications, design criteria, operational data, and approvals required to execute the work.\nDesign Reviews: Up to two (2) design review/revision cycles are included. Additional revisions arising from changes in scope or Client requirements will be billed at the agreed hourly rate.\nSoftware & QA/QC: Professional engineering software costs, internal quality assurance (QA/QC), and document checking are included in this quotation.\nTravel & Site Visits: Travel, accommodation, visa expenses, inspections, surveys, statutory fees, and third-party costs are excluded unless specifically stated.\nTaxes: Applicable taxes, duties, withholding taxes, or government levies shall be borne by the Client unless otherwise agreed in writing.\nIntellectual Property: All engineering calculations, models, drawings, reports, spreadsheets, and digital files remain the intellectual property of Primelisometrics Consultancy until full payment has been received.\nConfidentiality: Both parties shall maintain confidentiality of all technical and commercial information exchanged during the project.\nSuspension of Services: The Consultant reserves the right to suspend work on overdue invoices exceeding 30 calendar days without liability for schedule impacts.\nClient Delays: Delays caused by late information, approvals, or decisions from the Client may require adjustment of the project schedule and delivery dates.\nLiability: The Consultant's total liability arising from the services provided shall be limited to the value of the fees paid under this quotation.\nCurrency & Banking Charges: All payments shall be made in the agreed currency. Any international bank transfer charges shall be borne by the Client.\nAcceptance: Confirmation of this quotation by Purchase Order, signed acceptance, or written email approval shall constitute acceptance of these commercial conditions.",
      "created_at": "2026-07-09T10:47:25.899Z",
      "updated_at": "2026-07-09T13:20:10.149Z"
    }
